{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303690, "create_time": 1658246587, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "政府面对问题是先想着捂嘴，西方是拿着问题借题发挥攻击政府体制。我甚至可以部分理解从反政府上升到反民族的浪人，实在无法理解小粉红们闭眼甩锅的脑回路。", "timestamp": 1658246587}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303705, "create_time": 1658247081, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "15年本科入学的时候空气污染太严重，直接出现了哮喘，在家乡十几年都没得过。微积分课上老师带pm2.5检测仪，结果下课时发现都爆表了😅", "timestamp": 1658247081}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303754, "create_time": 1658250776, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "有没有可能，政府作为一个超越个人理性的存在，捂嘴反而是更有效的解决问题的方法", "timestamp": 1658250776}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303756, "create_time": 1658250851, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "当然如果你认为让大家都说话什么的社会更理性，就当我没说)", "timestamp": 1658250851}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303757, "create_time": 1658250919, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "当然如果你觉得中共的政权组织不是不是有效的，那也当我没说)", "timestamp": 1658250919}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303758, "create_time": 1658250956, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "当然如果你觉得社会存在的目的不是理性和高效，那也当我没说..)", "timestamp": 1658250956}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303760, "create_time": 1658251132, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "捂嘴是防止无意识的社会思潮被引导向非解决问题的方向...真的觉得中国的有很多人都有能力参与公开与直接的社会讨论么？", "timestamp": 1658251132}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303770, "create_time": 1658252038, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 笑拉了。中国不能搞民主制度是因为人民素质不够，这是我听过ccp讲的最好笑的笑话。", "timestamp": 1658252038}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303773, "create_time": 1658252373, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 一句话总结你的观点，刁民早该管了", "timestamp": 1658252373}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303833, "create_time": 1658275009, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: “中国人素质太差，不配有言论自由”", "timestamp": 1658275009}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303847, "create_time": 1658275323, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "这么大的人口基数下，出现什么事情都有可能", "timestamp": 1658275323}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303849, "create_time": 1658275392, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: \n>我甚至可以部分理解从反政府上升到反民族的浪人\n\n我刚说完我知道怎么回事，就有某人非要来给我解释他们的逻辑，无怪乎这么令人讨厌", "timestamp": 1658275392}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303852, "create_time": 1658275464, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "问题在国家面对这种严重问题时是否采取了行动去解决它，你看你也说了前几年很严重，现在这种情况在不断好转，说明国家的确是在采取行动解决的。“言论自由”能解决环保问题？", "timestamp": 1658275464}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303854, "create_time": 1658275683, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "政策好坏暂且不论，在国内谈“言论自由”很难不带有倾向性。小作文一写水军一刷就成正义了吗？我觉得这对解决实际问题没有什么帮助吧", "timestamp": 1658275683}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 303856, "create_time": 1658275727, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 问题在于，如果没有西方的指摘，政府也不会这么果